{"id":578235,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/02/【图说天朝】强国碰瓷之日常/","date":"2018-02-09T08:40:14Z","modified":"2018-02-09T08:40:48Z","title":"【图说天朝】强国碰瓷之日常","content":"<p><strong>【编者注】</strong>有中国厂商近日参加印度新德里汽车展的汽配展，抱怨主办方统一安排的中国展区地图没有包括台湾，认为是对方故意为之。与主办方沟通无果后，有中国参展商自己动手给地图画上了台湾部分。</p>\n<blockquote><p><a href=\"https://weibo.com/3939426052/G2cAz1Pk5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">@地瓜熊老六</a>：网友投稿：我们国内汽配商组团参加印度新德里汽配展，因为是标准摊位，外立面的装饰都是印度主办方负责，结果把中国区所有的外立面弄成了图一的样子（实际上按惯例都只需要标注地区就行，不用弄地图，主办方摆明故意的），我们国人要求改，印度不管，就都自己动手了，台湾属于中国这是不容妥协的！</p></blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/eacedf04ly1fo9bf9o6mmj20zk0qo40z.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-578236\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/eacedf04ly1fo9bf9o6mmj20zk0qo40z.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"413\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/eacedf04ly1fo9bf9o6mmj20zk0qo40z.jpg 1280w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/eacedf04ly1fo9bf9o6mmj20zk0qo40z-300x225.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/eacedf04ly1fo9bf9o6mmj20zk0qo40z-768x576.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/eacedf04ly1fo9bf9o6mmj20zk0qo40z-1024x768.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/eacedf04ly1fo9bf9zt2zj20zk0qo0vj.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-578237\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/eacedf04ly1fo9bf9zt2zj20zk0qo0vj.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"413\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/eacedf04ly1fo9bf9zt2zj20zk0qo0vj.jpg 1280w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/eacedf04ly1fo9bf9zt2zj20zk0qo0vj-300x225.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/eacedf04ly1fo9bf9zt2zj20zk0qo0vj-768x576.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/eacedf04ly1fo9bf9zt2zj20zk0qo0vj-1024x768.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>相关阅读：<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/05/%e3%80%90%e7%bd%91%e7%bb%9c%e6%b0%91%e8%ae%ae%e3%80%91%e4%b8%a4%e5%b2%b8%e7%bb%9f%e4%b8%80%e9%9d%a0%e7%a2%b0%e7%93%b7/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">【网络民议】两岸统一靠碰瓷</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><strong>附：充满民族优越感的原贴评论鉴赏</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/汽配展评论1.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-578238\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/汽配展评论1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"2568\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/汽配展评论1.jpg 1333w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/02/汽配展评论1-768x3944.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n","author":980,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,21627],"tags":[10218,12126,10268,8646,9481,22054]}